    {
      "content": [
        {
          "anchor": "overview",
          "level": 2,
          "text": "Overview",
          "type": "heading"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "During an AR session, RealityKit automatically lights your virtual objects",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "to match real-world lighting.",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "You can also explicitly add virtual lights that act upon your virtual content.",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "This is typically most useful outside of an AR session on iOS or macOS,",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "where your ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.RealityKit/documentation/RealityKit/RealityViewCameraContent",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.RealityKit/documentation/RealityKit/RealityViewCameraContent/camera",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "property is set to ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.RealityKit/documentation/RealityKit/RealityViewCamera/virtual",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "A directional light uniformly casts light along its local z-axis—specifically,",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "along ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "code": "[0, 0, -1]",
              "type": "codeVoice"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "This is equivalent to creating an ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.RealityKit/documentation/RealityKit/Entity",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ", and then adding",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "a ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.RealityKit/documentation/RealityKit/DirectionalLightComponent",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " to its ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.RealityKit/documentation/RealityKit/Entity/components",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " set.",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "Use the light’s ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.RealityKit/documentation/RealityKit/HasTransform/look(at:from:upVector:relativeTo:)",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "method to aim the light in a particular direction.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "You can configure the light’s color and intensity with the component properties",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "in ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.RealityKit/documentation/RealityKit/HasDirectionalLight/light",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "You can also control how or if it casts a ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.RealityKit/documentation/RealityKit/HasDirectionalLight/shadow",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        },
        {
          "inlineContent": [
            {
              "text": "A RealityKit scene can contain up to eight dynamic lights, which are",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "entities that contain a",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.RealityKit/documentation/RealityKit/SpotLightComponent",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ", ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.RealityKit/documentation/RealityKit/PointLightComponent",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ", or a ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "identifier": "doc://com.apple.RealityKit/documentation/RealityKit/DirectionalLightComponent",
              "isActive": true,
              "type": "reference"
            },
            {
              "text": ".",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": " ",
              "type": "text"
            },
            {
              "text": "This limit doesn’t include light from image-based lighting.",
              "type": "text"
            }
          ],
          "type": "paragraph"
        }
      ],
      "kind": "content"
    }
  ],
